{
  "texts": [
    "R3:The LIEF POST shall allow switching the USt for both Rücksendung Inland and Ausland.Example Test Scenario TS1: Delivery with Rücksendung Ausland.",
    "1) Open the LIEF POST app in VB mode.2) In VB mode, scan the packet with Rücksendung Ausland flag.",
    "3) Set the Zustellbasen to a town in the ZAB list.",
    "4) Long press on the packet and open the details.",
    "5) Turn the Switch to ON for the 18% USt."
  ]
}